The '''Kalindan System Defense Force''' was part of the military commanded by the monarchs of the [[Kalinda system/Legends|Kalinda system]].

==History==
The Kalindan System Defense Force fought alongside the [[Kalindan Deep Space Fleet]] when [[Battle of Kalinda|faced]] with an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] invasion of the [[Kalinda system/Legends|Kalinda system]]. Their attempts to control the system failed, as the Kalindan forces were victorious.

